1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,720
Esto...

2
00:00:00,720 --> 00:00:01,760
estaba en la calle.

3
00:00:01,760 --> 00:00:02,760
En plenas Fallas.

4
00:00:02,760 --> 00:00:03,360
Mirad.

5
00:00:03,360 --> 00:00:04,200
Petardos,

6
00:00:04,200 --> 00:00:05,080
ninots,

7
00:00:05,080 --> 00:00:05,400
fiesta por

8
00:00:05,400 --> 00:00:06,360
todas partes...

9
00:00:06,360 --> 00:00:07,040
y entre medio,

10
00:00:07,040 --> 00:00:07,840
cosas increíbles

11
00:00:07,840 --> 00:00:08,920
tiradas en la acera.

12
00:00:08,920 --> 00:00:09,760
Es que en Fallas

13
00:00:09,760 --> 00:00:11,040
la gente limpia,

14
00:00:11,040 --> 00:00:11,680
renueva,

15
00:00:11,680 --> 00:00:12,760
cambia muebles...

16
00:00:12,760 --> 00:00:13,320
y la ciudad

17
00:00:13,320 --> 00:00:14,200
se llena de tesoros

18
00:00:14,200 --> 00:00:15,040
que nadie ve.

19
00:00:15,040 --> 00:00:15,400
Solo hay

20
00:00:15,400 --> 00:00:16,000
que fijarse.

21
00:00:16,000 --> 00:00:16,680
Pues yo ya voy

22
00:00:16,680 --> 00:00:17,080
preparado

23
00:00:17,080 --> 00:00:18,440
para estos momentos.

24
00:00:18,440 --> 00:00:18,840
Lo veo,

25
00:00:18,840 --> 00:00:20,040
lo subo a Givore,

26
00:00:20,040 --> 00:00:20,520
y en nada

27
00:00:20,520 --> 00:00:21,280
alguien del barrio

28
00:00:21,280 --> 00:00:22,200
lo descubre.

29
00:00:22,200 --> 00:00:22,840
Mientras la ciudad

30
00:00:22,840 --> 00:00:23,480
celebra,

31
00:00:23,480 --> 00:00:24,880
vecinos conectando

32
00:00:24,880 --> 00:00:26,080
sin conocerse.

33
00:00:26,080 --> 00:00:27,000
Segunda vida

34
00:00:27,000 --> 00:00:27,720
para todo.

35
00:00:27,720 --> 00:00:28,400
Así que ojo

36
00:00:28,400 --> 00:00:29,200
esta semana.

37
00:00:29,200 --> 00:00:29,560
Las calles

38
00:00:29,560 --> 00:00:30,200
de Valencia

39
00:00:30,200 --> 00:00:31,080
durante Fallas

40
00:00:31,080 --> 00:00:31,880
son una mina.

41
00:00:31,880 --> 00:00:32,240
¿Habéis encontrado

42
00:00:32,240 --> 00:00:32,840
algo bueno

43
00:00:32,840 --> 00:00:33,600
estos días?

44
00:00:33,600 --> 00:00:34,040
Contádmelo

45
00:00:34,040 --> 00:00:34,640
en comentarios.

46
00:00:34,640 --> 00:00:35,440
Quiero ver

47
00:00:35,440 --> 00:00:36,240
vuestros hallazgos

48
00:00:36,240 --> 00:00:37,000
falleros.

